    "body": "Closes #39213\r\n\r\n### Problem\r\n\r\n`ex_detach()` has a stub for `:detach!` that errors with `\"bang (!) not supported yet\"`. There is no way for one UI to kick the others off a shared Nvim server.\r\n\r\n### Solution\r\n\r\n`:detach!` disconnects every UI except the caller's, keeping the server running and the caller attached. No-op with one UI. Errors with `E5768: No UI attached` when no UI is attached.",
    "closed_at": null,
